{"tid":1649751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不分化不割蓆唔係免死金牌","createTime":"2019-10-12T18:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T00:26:31.000Z","uid":82917,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0832a89388129de364e36aece8d996a5459ec4","tid":1649751,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">預咗俾人屌我分化撚</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FZq6Z2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FZq6Z2.jpg&h=4f99ecd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/770qnyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F770qnyo.jpg&h=50cff9b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔撚好同我講咁撚樣叫無預謀呀！<br />\n講撚到食tg係玩泥沙咁撚兒戲<br />\n你班閪人個腦裝屎㗎？<br />\n手足？我手你老母！<br />\n每個手足上場都搵條命去博<br />\n打卡撚叫同路人咩請問？<br />\n咁撚樣講不如話示威區經過啲藍絲都係同路人呀！<br />\n痴撚線，唔係講分唔分化嘅問題<br />\n呢啲左膠打卡垃撚圾行為一定要屌撚醒，唔係會有破窗效應唔係會有破窗效應<br />\n得閒無事又走幾條mk仔女出嚟搞場大龍鳳嘻嘻哈哈博上報<br />\n俾外媒影到會點呀？對唔對得住被捕嗰2000人？<br />\n有無諗過坐緊監嘅政治犯？<br />\n仲有，有啲義士已經無得再慶生⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大個啦，做事之前諗清楚後果啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4090c56ae6e1e0baa8ef596f465655f45a9ac0e","tid":1649751,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"推班條傻閪同埋佢班豬朋狗友睇到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69962c3b0bc013a16968002625a5fd0f4e7e423e","tid":1649751,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a684da7cd30abbd1cd91eb6232db07b3bfeaa37","tid":1649751,"uid":151966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"大局